## Workflow Trigger Integration

### API Endpoint

Handlers trigger workflows via `POST /workflows/run`:

```python
payload = {
    "workflow_name": "typosquat_analysis",
    "program_name": "example",
    "description": "Analyze typosquat domains",
    "parameters": {
        "domains": ["domain1.com", "domain2.com"]
    }
}

response = requests.post(
    f"{api_url}/workflows/run",
    json=payload,
    headers={
        "Authorization": f"Bearer {api_key}",
        "Content-Type": "application/json"
    },
    timeout=30
)
```

### Response

```json
{
    "workflow_id": "uuid",
    "id": "execution_id",
    "status": "queued"
}
```

